  <developerConceptualDocument xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <introduction>
      <para>Error CVT0003: Invalid or missing schema version</para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Cause</title>
      <content>
        <para>This error is caused by a missing schema version property in the
source project.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Solution</title>
      <content>
        <para>The most likely cause of this error is that you have attempted
to load a help file builder version 1.7.0.0 or earlier project file that is
not valid.  Check the file to be sure that it is a help file builder project
file.  If you are unable to solve the problem based on the reported error,
open a work item in the <token>SHFB</token> project at CodePlex containing
the details from the error message.  Attach the affected source project as an
example.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

